OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA hot day with plenty of
OL,6,Fsunshine, staying a little cooler
OL,7,Falong the coast. The sunshine turning
OL,8,Fa little hazy during the afternoon. A
OL,9,Fgentle breeze strengthens later before
OL,10,Feasing once more by the evening.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FClouding over but remaining
OL,13,Fdry for most of the night, a few spots
OL,14,Fof rain possible by the early morning
OL,15,Fin places.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSaturday:FAny cloud and rain should
OL,18,Fquickly clear to give a bright, sunny
OL,19,Fand warm day. Staying a little cooler
OL,20,Falong the coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
